      "settings": {
        "heading": "ABOUT US",
        "text_content": "<p>Fansē a good story? Ours started in a salon. <br/><br/>With a pulse for the finer things in life, we create professional-driven formulas to make you look and feel<br/>like you just left your favorite stylist’s chair. We’ve captured that “just-got-my-hair-done” confidence and bottled it for everyday use. <br/><br/>Because a great hair day shouldn’t always require an appointment, just a few products you’ll actually want<br/>to reach for.<br/></p>",
