      "name": "About Grid",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "BEHIND OUR NAME",
        "text_content": "<p>Fansē is more than a name. <br/><br/>It’s the luxury of taking time for yourself. <br/>The confidence in knowing your hair will look great. <br/>A moment of ease and indulgence. <br/><br/>Fansē began as a space where people came to be pampered and left feeling their best. Now it’s also a line <br/>of products that bring that same experience into your daily routine, so everyone can feel a little fansē, any day<br/>of the week.<br/></p>",
