      "name": "About Grid",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "ABOUT OUR FOUNDER",
        "text_content": "<p>With over a decade of experience behind the chair, Tori Elyse has lived and breathed haircare for most of her life. <br/><br/>Since founding Fansē Salon, what began as just one chair and one shampoo bowl turned into something much bigger. She’s made a name for herself, not only as our founder, but as an entrepreneur, stylist, educator, and content creator. Simply put, she knows a thing or two about great hair.<br/><br/>With natural curls of her own, Tori has always understood the real-life challenges of styling at home, especially when it comes to getting a sleek look without relying on a whole lineup of gels, creams, and sprays. After years of clients asking how to master the perfect slick-back, she set out to find a better way. <br/><br/>Her solution? Fansē Potion. <br/><br/><a href=\"#middle\" title=\"#middle\">And voilà! </a><br/><br/><a href=\"#right\" title=\"#right\">The rest was history.</a></p>",
